snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy:

A man comes to Bhide's house asking after his Papad business. Very enthusiastically they show him all the Papads they sell.Finally after listening to all the details the man reveals to them that he simply came there to know the rates of the Papads for the business his daughter has started.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 906
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2025  #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta #jethalalmemes #tmkocmemes #jethalalcomedy #food #foodies #foodie #gokuldham #fullepisode #comedyvideos #foodlover 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Ke Foodies' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cT5G12J5Crvkt1XPr2dP5iG

snippet.description:
#GhumHaiKisikeyPyaarMein #GHKKPM #SaasBahuAurSaazish #SBS #aditiarorasawant 

In Ghum Hai Kisikey Pyaar Meiin, the character Savi is introduced as Sai and Virat’s daughter. Savi brings a new dimension to the story as she becomes a bridge and a source of emotional complexity between her estranged parents, Sai and Virat. Her presence challenges Virat's loyalty to his family and reignites unresolved feelings between him and Sai. Rajat is another recent character who brings twists to the plot, affecting the dynamics between the main characters and creating new conflicts. Both Savi and Rajat play pivotal roles in evolving the storyline, deepening the emotional layers of the show, and introducing new conflicts that keep the characters—and viewers—on their toes.

Episode 4297: Bapuji's Rescue
--------------------------------------------------------

snippet.title: EGG BONDA | MUTTAI BONDA | Road Side Evening Snacks Recipe Cooking In Village | Bajji Street Food
snippet.description:
In this video, we bring you the ultimate recipe for Egg Bonda (Muttai Bonda), a beloved roadside evening snack that everyone enjoys! Watch as we prepare this crispy, golden-brown delight in a traditional village setting, using fresh ingredients and time-honored cooking techniques.

The Egg Bonda is made by coating perfectly boiled eggs with a spiced gram flour batter and frying them to perfection. This mouthwatering snack is best enjoyed hot, with an evening. Whether you're a fan of street food or looking for a quick and tasty recipe to try at home, this video has you covered!

Get a glimpse of authentic village-style cooking and join us as we prepare this classic Indian snack in a scenic, peaceful atmosphere.

snippet.title: Every Web Series in Seconds | Take A Break
snippet.description:
Ever wished you could watch an entire web series in just a few seconds? Well, we made it happen! 🎬😂
In Every Web Series in Seconds, we take the most popular Indian and international web series and summarize their entire plots in the quickest, most hilarious way possible. Get ready for a rollercoaster of rapid recaps, savage one-liners, and absurdly accurate summaries that will leave you laughing out loud. Whether you’re a binge-watcher or someone who never made it past episode one, this video is for you!
Which web series do you think we nailed? Let us know in the comments! 🤣🔥

पुलिस FIR के मुताबिक :

सैफ अली खान के घर में चोरी करने वाले व्यक्ति को लेकर जो बयान दर्ज किए गए हैं उसके मुताबिक 56 वर्षीय सैफ अली खान के घर की हाउस मेड ने बताया कि उसे बाथरूम के पास अचानक कोई परछाई नजर आई उसे लगा कि करीना शायद अपने छोटे बेटे को देखने आए होगी लेकिन उन्हें बाद में शक हुआ तो वह... आगे गई अचानक एक 35 से 40 वर्षीय अज्ञात व्यक्ति ने महिला के ऊपर हमला कर दिया और धारदार हथियार दिखाते हुए चुप रहने के लिए कहा इसी बीच दूसरी मेड भी आ गई... आरोपी से पूछा गया कि उसे क्या चाहिए उसने कहा कि एक करोड रुपए... इसी दौरान अगर बात की जाए तो सैफ अली खान जो बारहवें फ्लोर पर रहते हैं, वह भी नीचे आ गए उन्होंने जब देखा तो अज्ञात आरोपी और सैफ के बीच हाथापाई हुई जिसमें सैफ को शरीर के अलग-अलग हिस्सों पर छह जगहों पर चोट लगी.. जिसमें से एक नुकीला हथियार टूट कर सैफ के शरीर में भी अटक गया... इसी दौरान आरोपी को उन लोगों ने दूसरे कमरे में बंद भी कर दिया लेकिन जब सैफ को ज्यादा चोट लगी थी तब मेड और फैमिली के बाकी स्टाफ मेंबर्स ने इब्राहिम को बुलाया इब्राहिम और सारा अली खान भी आठवीं मंजिल पर ही रहते हैं वह ऊपर आए और सैफ अली खान को लेकर ऑटो में अस्पताल गए... अगर बात की जाए गाड़ी की तो उसे वक्त परिवार में कोई भी ड्राइवर मौजूद नहीं था और ऑटोमेटिक इलेक्ट्रिक वाहन फिलहाल किसी को चलाना नहीं आता था इसलिए आनन फानन में सैफ को लेकर वे लोग लीलावती अस्पताल पहुंचे।

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4299 - Dushmano ka Samna kar Society wapis Laute Bapuji?! | Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada

snippet.title: Battle of the Chefs: 2v2 Cooking Competition Gone Wild!
snippet.description:
🔥 Welcome to the Ultimate Cooking Showdown! 🔥

In this epic 2v2 cooking competition, we challenged two teams to create the most delicious Paneer Rolls ever! With only a limited time to cook and creativity as their main ingredient, the battle gets intense in the kitchen. 🍳

Will it be Team Blue or Team Red that impresses the judges and takes home the victory? 🏆 Watch as the teams bring their A-game, face hilarious kitchen disasters, and surprise us with their culinary skills!

👨‍🍳 The Rules:

- Both teams must prepare Paneer Rolls.
- The team with the tastiest and most creative rolls wins!

💬 Let us know in the comments which team's rolls you would love to try!

📢 Don't forget to LIKE, SUBSCRIBE, and hit the NOTIFICATION BELL to never miss an exciting challenge! 🎉

snippet.title: रावण - अंगद प्रसंग | Dr Kumar Vishwas | अपने-अपने राम | नागपुर
snippet.description:
अगर साहस, सकारात्मकता, संवाद की कलात्मकता व सात्विकता की शक्ति को केशव की काव्य-धारा का सानिध्य मिल जाए तो उस पूर्ण संगम में रामकथा का रस अनायास ही शतगुणित हो जाता है। अपने-अपने राम ऊर्जा-सत्र में रावण-अंगद संवाद का यह प्रसंग आप सबकी आस्तिकता को सादर समर्पित हैं। 😊🙏🏻
#kumarvishwas #apneapneram #nagpur #ramayan 

Follow us on :- 

YouTube :- http://youtube.com/KumarVishwas
Facebook :- https://www.facebook.com/KumarVishwas
Twitter :- https://twitter.com/DrKumarVishwas
Instagram :- https://www.instagram.com/KumarVishwas

Subscribe To Our Other YouTube Channels:-

Apne Apne Ram    : https://www.youtube.com/@ApneApneRamOfficial
  
The KV Studio        : https://www.youtube.com/@TheKVStudio

Apne Apne Shyam : https://www.youtube.com/@ApneApneShyamOfficial

-------------------------------------------------------------------
About Dr Kumar Vishwas :

The people who make history are the ones who not only give their life to their career but also give their career a new life. When the career is that of a poet, every step is a risk. Kumar Vishwas is one such poet who has gifted himself an era of such a popularity which other poets cant’t even dream of.
Kumar Vishwas is a poet who went beyond the stereotypical norms of ‘Kavi Sammelan’ or poetic functions and made it a performer’s stage. He has mastered and excelled in all aspects in whatever he has done. Dr Kumar Vishwas has been doing this since years just with a mic and his poems and wits in his soulful voice.
His popularity can be guessed by the fact that the audience sings his verses with him, he has crafted a new dimension by rejuvenating the structure and mechanics of Hindi poetry and Kavi Sammelan.
 
Recently, Dr. Kumar Vishwas has started hosting energy sessions popularly Known as Apne Apne Ram and Apne Apne Shyam where he talks about life skills of Shri Ram’s and Shri Krishna's life, and the applicability of the same in one’s own life to over come the challenges and social concerns we come across in our life.

Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche

Hunda vi ae hone vi ae saade charche
Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche


Baade rooh de rangeen Munde

Saade bad scene hunde
Sire de ae dith
Tappe saadi leek
Fer malo mali malo mali malo mali
Sir  chad jaande parche

Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche

Tu beeta hua kal
Mera flow jaise Future 
Underground chalu jaise mein
Mewat ka koi Buchter
Jo bars meri week thi 
Vo tere liye tutor hai 
Tu ankh band kre baitha jaise koi kabootar hai
 Gangster sune mere gaane baithe jail mein
Mein Dm Nahi krta bars karu mail mein
Naam k hi rapper hai yeah sun tu detail mein
Labelo pe dekhe hai zameer inke sale mein
Luck te nahi khade hai hukk the
Mein Fuck na deyu Koi deta jo takht pe
Vakht hai mera inki jamante japt hai
Mere doore Dhari inki amante girvi
Inke pale daale kuch ni 
Yeah baat maare fir bhi

Delhi k buwane tak
Naam le diye tu tanne pahochade tikane tak

Bhai kisse ka digaya nahi digda mein
Jab tak sar pr bhole ka mere hath hai hath hai
Ehna hoya ni siyana 
Har cheez te mein bola
Kaam di ae bukh fame da ni rola
Buss dekhi chalo jatt kidda thal de barola
Jurta naa jande ae takh palte

snippet.title: రే బుల్లిరాజు ఏం చేశావ్‌రా: Director Anil Ravipudi Speech | Venkatesh | Asianet News Telugu
snippet.description:
విక్టరీ వెంకటేష్‌, అనిల్‌ రావిపూడి కాంబినేషన్‌లో వచ్చిన మూడో సినిమా సంక్రాంతికి వస్తున్నాం. ఈ సంక్రాంతికి విడుదలైన సంక్రాంతికి వస్తున్నాం మూవీ సూపర్‌ సక్సెస్‌ అందుకుంది. దీంతో చిత్ర బృందం సంబరాల్లో మునిపోయింది. ఈ సందర్భంగా హైదరాబాద్‌లో నిర్వహించిన 'బ్లాక్‌బస్టర్‌ పొంగల్‌ జాతర' ఈవెంట్‌లో డైరెక్టర్‌ అనిల్‌ రావిపూడి మాట్లాడారు. సంక్రాంతికి వస్తున్నాం సినిమాని సూపర్‌ హిట్‌ చేసిన ప్రేక్షకులకు కృతజ్ఞతలు తెలిపారు.

snippet.title: R G Kar News : আমি যদি ধর্ষণ করতাম ...রায় ঘোষণার পর বিস্ফোরক Sanjay | Bangla News
snippet.description:
R G Kar News : আর জি করে দোষী সাব্যস্ত সঞ্জয় রাই। সোমবার সাজা ঘোষণা করবে আদালত। তরুণী চিকিৎসকের ধর্ষণ-খুনে রায়। সঞ্জয়কে দোষী সাব্যস্ত শিয়ালদা আদালতের। ৫ মাস পর আর জি করের রায়। ৯ অগাস্ট ২০২৪- আর জি করে ধর্ষণ-খুন। পরদিনই সঞ্জয়কে গ্রেফতার Kolkata Police র।

#rgkarnews #rgkarmedicalcollege #rgkarverdict #sanjayrai #cbi #sealdahcourt #banglanews #news18bangla 
n180c_kolkata
